cdata.name: VirtaCoin
cdata.desc: VirtaCoin, formerly PayBox.me/VirtaPay, enables instant payments to anyone, anywhere in the world.VirtaCoin offers a printed cash-note system, which can help real-life users in adopting to cryptocurrencies through a familiar method: paper money. Altough VTA is Proof of Work currency, you can also earn interest by being involved in VirtaCoin Kiva Fund.
